The paper deals with recommendation systems, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of matrix factorization and regression models also suggests a focus on the subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) as it aims to improve the accuracy of recommendations. The use of clustering algorithms and the analysis of real-world datasets suggest a focus on data science (cs.DS) and the subfield of social and information networks (cs.SI).
